creator: JservxTechnologies
descriptionHtml:
Abu (Igbo Christian Hymn) app is the popularly known hymnal known as "Abu Iji Ekpere Chineke" by the Igbo community at large.


Abu is an Igbo Christian Hymn app available for Android phones. Abu is designed for the Igbo tribe around the world to join worship in their dialect.


Why use ABU:
• Offline access to hymns.
• Easy to use.
• Search Igbo hymns by song number and title.
• Has support to copy any Igbo hymn of your choice, paste or share anywhere.
• Clear and friendly learning interface.
• Complete Igbo Christian Hymns.
• Supports a wide range of screen sizes.
• Has audio tunes for some hymns.
• The Igbo Christian hymn app is free. However, Network providers might charge for data on an update.

Users say:
"Abu- A worship companion" - Rev Obinna
"Abu- Fantastic collection"- Ngerem Bertram
"Really nice app"- Doris Ejide


Enjoy your favorite Igbo christian hymn anytime and anywhere.

Like and talk to us on Facebook @AbuIgboChristianHymn
Download now to access all Igbo Christian hymn 24/7.

...Join the praise in Igbo dialect. Get your Igbo Christian Hymn app.

Proudly Nigerian.

title: ABU (Igbo Christian Hymn) -Abu Iji Ekpere Chineke

creator: JservxTechnologies
descriptionHtml:
Abu (Igbo Christian Hymn) app is the popularly known hymnal known as "Abu Iji Ekpere Chineke" by the Igbo community at large.
It is the Igbo hymn book used in the Anglican communion.

Abu is an Igbo Christian Hymn app available for Android phones. Abu is designed for the Igbo tribe around the world to join worship in their dialect. Few hymn tunes as available to be stream online.


Why use ABU:
• Offline access to Igbo hymns.
• Features audio tunes for some hymns.
• Easy to use.
• Search Igbo hymns by song number, title and first line of English equivalent.
• Has support to copy any Igbo hymn of your choice, paste or share anywhere.
• Clear and friendly learning interface.
• Complete Igbo Christian Hymns.
• Supports a wide range of screen sizes.
• The Igbo Christian hymn app is free. However, Network providers might charge for data on an update.

Users say:
"Abu- A worship companion" - Rev Obinna
"Abu- Fantastic collection"- Ngerem Bertram
"Really nice app"- Doris Ejide
"Very necessary to my daily worship" Kelechi Godson

Enjoy your favorite Igbo Christian hymn anytime and anywhere.

Like and talk to us on Facebook @AbuIgboChristianHymn
Download now to access all Igbo Christian hymn 24/7.

Join the praise in Igbo dialect. Get your Igbo Christian Hymn app.

To join click the link below.
